			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Resolution:</strong> Search your application&#39;s CSS for anything
				that may be targeting <code>rux-checkbox-group</code> directly and replace
				with the appropriate CSS Shadow Part.
			</p>
			<p></p><div class="breaking-change__code">
				<div class="breaking-change__code__block">
					<div class="breaking-change__code__title">v6</div>
					<Code
						lang="css"
						code={`
	rux-checkbox-group {
		color: red;
		font-family: Arial;
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		line-height: 1;
		letter-spacing: 0.3em;
	}
							`}
					/>
				</div>
